\i\b Cards
\i0\b0 : After each turn in which a player conquers at least one country, the player gets a card.  There is one card for each country, and each card has a symbol on it: a soldier, a horse, or a cannon.  At the beginning of each turn, the player has the option of turning in sets of cards for extra armies.  A set of cards is three cards which have either one of each symbol, or three of the same symbol.  There are three options for the worth of card sets.\
