\i\b \cf0 Losing
\i0\b0 :  A player is out of the game when they no longer occupy any countries.  The opponent who conquered the player's last country gets all the player's unused cards.\
\

\i\b Winning
\i0\b0 :  A player wins when he occupies all the countries on the map.\
